  <brief_title>Abdominal Binder Study to Decrease Postoperative Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Controlled Randomized Trial Examining the Ability of the Mott Compression Bonder to Decrease Postoperative Pain in Gynecologic Abdominal Laparotomy Patients.</official_title>
